<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">我現在呀，<delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正在想著今年<delay8 />
一定要實現自己的夢想呢～！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是出道當偶像啦，<delay20 />進軍全世界啦，<delay20 />
創作歌曲達成百萬銷售記錄啦……<delay20 />
啊！還有還有，<delay8 />要和我的白馬王子<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay8 />真是的！<delay20 />
夢想太多了，根本說不完嘛～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望今年的新年初夢<delay20 />
可以夢到一個好兆頭～！<pageBreak /><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一，<delay8 />富士山。<delay8 />二，老鷹。<delay20 />三，<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 /><tag a="110" b="10" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得對<tag a="110" b="4" />來說，<delay8 />
比起一和二，還是三更適合你唷！<delay40 />
祝你有個好夢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新年日本的電視節目上，<delay20 />
大家都穿著可愛的和服，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來超華麗的，讓人心情都變好了呢～！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近好像還流行很多不同種類的花紋，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像復古風、現代風之類的，<delay8 />每個都很時尚耶。<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也得好好跟上呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～！<delay40 />為什麼一到新年，<delay8 />
就會覺得<delay8 />年糕這麼好吃呢～！？<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是日式烤年糕<delay20 />就有砂糖、<delay8 />醬油、<delay8 />
海苔、<delay8 />黃豆粉、<delay8 />還有奶油……<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這麼多口味，<delay8 />不得了啦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在日本，說到新年<delay8 />就會想到板羽球！<delay40 />
就用我最喜歡的沙灘排球技巧<delay20 />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來個旋轉發球好了～！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />身為偶像，<delay20 /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然不能
輸到被畫上滿臉塗鴉呀！<delay40 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來我得全力以赴了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>